      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">metasomatic rock</skos:prefLabel>
      <dct:description xml:lang="en">Rock that has fabric and composition indicating open-system mineralogical and chemical changes in response to interaction with a fluid phase, typically water rich.</dct:description>
