      <dct:title xml:lang="en">carbonate sediment</dct:title>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">carbonate sediment</skos:prefLabel>
      <dct:description xml:lang="en">Sediment in which at least 50 percent of the primary and/or recrystallized constituents are composed of one (or more) of the carbonate minerals calcite, aragonite and dolomite, in particles of intrabasinal origin.</dct:description>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Sediment in which at least 50 percent of the primary and/or recrystallized constituents are composed of one (or more) of the carbonate minerals calcite, aragonite and dolomite, in particles of intrabasinal origin.</skos:definition>
