      <dct:title xml:lang="en">tonalite</dct:title>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">tonalite</skos:prefLabel>
      <dct:description xml:lang="en">Granitoid consisting of quartz and intermediate plagioclase, usually with biotite and amphibole. Includes rocks defined modally in QAPF field 5; ratio of plagioclase to total feldspar is greater than 0.9.</dct:description>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Granitoid consisting of quartz and intermediate plagioclase, usually with biotite and amphibole. Includes rocks defined modally in QAPF field 5; ratio of plagioclase to total feldspar is greater than 0.9.</skos:definition>
