      <dct:title xml:lang="en">phonolite</dct:title>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">phonolite</skos:prefLabel>
      <dct:description xml:lang="en">Phonolitoid in which the plagioclase to total feldspar ratio is less than 0.1. Rock consists of alkali feldspar, feldspathoid minerals, and mafic minerals.</dct:description>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Phonolitoid in which the plagioclase to total feldspar ratio is less than 0.1. Rock consists of alkali feldspar, feldspathoid minerals, and mafic minerals.</skos:definition>
