      <dct:title xml:lang="en">sapropel</dct:title>
      <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">sapropel</skos:prefLabel>
      <dct:description xml:lang="en">Jelly like organic rich sediment composed of plant remains, usually algal. Liptinite to Inertinite ratio is greater than one (Economic Commission for Europe, Committee on Sustainable Energy- United Nations (ECE-UN), 1998, International Classification of in-Seam Coals: Energy 19, 41 pp.)</dct:description>
      <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Jelly like organic rich sediment composed of plant remains, usually algal. Liptinite to Inertinite ratio is greater than one (Economic Commission for Europe, Committee on Sustainable Energy- United Nations (ECE-UN), 1998, International Classification of in-Seam Coals: Energy 19, 41 pp.)</skos:definition>
      <skos:broader rdf:resource="http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/codelist/LithologyValue/organicRichSediment"/>
